# MQTT ACL — silno-dom-server
#
# IMPORTANT: Default rules (no `user` prefix) apply to anonymous clients only
# and MUST appear BEFORE any `user` block. Mosquitto has no "end user" marker —
# anything after `user X` belongs to X until the next `user` line or EOF.

# Anonymous clients (MOiO device — no MQTT auth support in firmware)
# Restricted to moio/# namespace only.
topic readwrite moio/#

# Authenticated clients (bridge, web app use MQTT_USER/MQTT_PASS)
user silnodom
topic readwrite #
